data.description: Welcome to your dream home in West Haverstraw, NY! This spacious 2 bedroom 1 bathroom gem boasts an updated kitchen and bathroom for modern convenience and the partially finished basement offers extra space for your needs. The inviting family room, features vaulted ceilings and skylights and seamlessly connects to the fully fenced backyard. Located closely to Peck's Pond, minutes from beautifulBowline Park and the majestic Hudson River. The home is also close to the bus and Haverstraw Ferry.  Don't miss out on this perfect blend of comfort and style!
